<h2>nlirms: Non-Life Insurance Rate-Making System</h2>
<p>Design of non-life insurance rate-making system with a frequency and a severity component based on the a posteriori criteria. The rate-making system is a general form of bonus-malus system introduced by Lemaire (1995), &lt;<a href="https://doi.org/10.1007%2F978-94-011-0631-3">doi:10.1007/978-94-011-0631-3</a>&gt; and Frangos and Vrontos (2001), &lt;<a href="https://doi.org/10.2143%2FAST.31.1.991">doi:10.2143/AST.31.1.991</a>&gt;.</p>
